data.description: Remodeled 2 bedroom 1 bath cottage, concrete block, painted inside and outside. New roof. New central heating and air. New water heater and w/d connections. Remodeled kitchen: floor, paint, door, appliances, cabinets, counters, sink, faucets and plumbing, vent hood, window, lighting. Remodeled bath: paint, resurfaced tub, tub surround, commode vanity lighting. New carpet. Ceramic tile kitchen and bath. Extra storage out back door, which is also a rear entry to "L" shaped laundry/storage room, new water heater. Lovely front porch. Large sodded rear yard. New knobs and locks. New blinds. Smooth ceilings. Large closets. Living area open to kitchen. Cute cottage with wide halls, feeling of spaciousness. This home is a must see...  Updated items: Architectural Dimensional Roof 5/2020; Current, New paint in and out; bath vanity 8/2020; reglazed bathtub 11/2020; kitchen cabinets 10/16/2020; carpet 10/2020; appliances, water heater 10/20/2020; sink and counters 11/2020; tub surround 11/2020; Weather Maker 2 ton, 14 S.E.E.R air handler with heat strips 2 drain float safety switches, bleach/vinegar port 12/2020
